result:
<st-modal
  title="入库"
  @ok="onSubmit"
  v-model="show"
  :loading="loading.stockWarehouse"
>
  <st-table
    :columns="columns"
    :dataSource="skuList"
    rowKey="sku_id"
    :page="false"
  >
    <template slot="stock_amount" slot-scope="customRender, record">
      <st-input-number
        v-model="record.stock_amount"
        :float="true"
        style="width:110px;"
      ></st-input-number>
    </template>
    <template slot="remark" slot-scope="customRender, record">
      <a-input
        v-model="record.remark"
        :float="true"
        style="width:110px;"
      ></a-input>
    </template>
  </st-table>
</st-modal>
